sily move around. You\u2019ll need a little bit of fat in the pan, like oil or butter, to keep your food from sticking."),mdx("h2",null,"How to roast"),mdx("p",null,"Roasting is a type of baking that uses high heat in an open oven. Roasting uses dry heat to cook food with a high temperature and a longer time. It is used for meat and vegetables, but not for other types of food."),mdx("p",null,"When roasting something, you want to make sure you have enough space in the oven so that it can circulate properly and cook evenly. You may need to do multiple batches, depending on the size of your oven and the amount of food you want to roast."),mdx("h2",null,"How to grill"),mdx("p",null,"Grilling is a dry-heat cooking method that uses direct heat to cook food. You place food on a grill over direct heat. Grills are usually out in the open, but you can also grill indoors on a stove or a grill that is specially made for indoor grilling."),mdx("p",null,"When grilling, you want to make sure that the grill is clean and oiled so that the food doesn\u2019t stick. You may also want to cover the grill to trap in the heat and keep the food warm until it is cooked."),mdx("h2",null,"Summing up"),mdx("p",null,"Cooking is a skill that can save your life if you ever find yourself in a situation where you have to rely on your own resources for food. Knowing how to cook can also help you save money, be healthier, and have more control over your diet."),mdx("p",null,"The best way to learn how to cook is to pick an easy recipe and practice it until you get it right. You can also try to combine different techniques to create something new. Cooking is an art form, so you can really get creative with it!"))}MDXContent.isMDXComponent=!0;

